<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Кошкар-Ата — Радиоактивное озеро Казахстана</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;600;700&family=Courier+Prime:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --red:    #E63946;
    --amber:  #F4A261;
    --teal:   #4ECDC4;
    --navy:   #0D1B2A;
    --navy2:  #1B2A3C;
    --card:   #162032;
    --white:  #F0EDE8;
    --muted:  #7B96B2;
    --green:  #52B788;
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    cursor: default;
  }

  /* ── Grain overlay ── */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9999;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 1.2rem 4rem;
    background: rgba(13,27,42,0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(230,57,70,0.2);
    transition: background 0.3s;
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: var(--red);
  }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--red); }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  #hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 0 4rem;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 80% 50%, rgba(230,57,70,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 60% at 10% 80%, rgba(78,205,196,0.06) 0%, transparent 60%),
      var(--navy);
  }

  /* Animated radiation rings */
  .rings {
    position: absolute;
    right: 8%;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 480px;
    height: 480px;
  }
  .ring {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(230,57,70,0.3);
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    animation: pulse-ring 3s ease-out infinite;
  }
  .ring:nth-child(1) { width: 120px; height: 120px; animation-delay: 0s; border-color: rgba(230,57,70,0.7); }
  .ring:nth-child(2) { width: 200px; height: 200px; animation-delay: 0.5s; }
  .ring:nth-child(3) { width: 300px; height: 300px; animation-delay: 1s; }
  .ring:nth-child(4) { width: 420px; height: 420px; animation-delay: 1.5s; }
  @keyframes pulse-ring {
    0%   { opacity: 0.8; transform: translate(-50%,-50%) scale(0.95); }
    100% { opacity: 0; transform: translate(-50%,-50%) scale(1.05); }
  }

  .rad-symbol {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 80px; height: 80px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .rad-symbol svg { animation: slow-spin 20s linear infinite; }
  @keyframes slow-spin {
    from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
    to   { transform: rotate(360deg); }
  }

  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 600px; }

  .hero-tag {
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--red);
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }
  .hero-tag::before {
    content: '';
    display: inline-block;
    width: 30px; height: 1px;
    background: var(--red);
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 9vw, 8rem);
    line-height: 0.92;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
  }
  h1 span { color: var(--red); }

  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 480px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
    background: var(--red);
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .hero-cta:hover { background: #c0222f; transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .hero-cta svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; }

  .scroll-hint {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2.5rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    animation: bounce 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
    50%       { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(6px); }
  }

  /* ── STATS STRIP ── */
  #stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(230,57,70,0.2);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(230,57,70,0.2);
  }
  .stat-item {
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(230,57,70,0.15);
    background: var(--card);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: background 0.3s;
  }
  .stat-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .stat-item:hover { background: #1c2d42; }
  .stat-item::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--red);
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transition: transform 0.3s;
    transform-origin: left;
  }
  .stat-item:hover::after { transform: scaleX(1); }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 3.8rem;
    color: var(--red);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }
  .stat-unit {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .stat-item.amber .stat-num { color: var(--amber); }

  /* ── SECTION SHARED ── */
  section { padding: 7rem 4rem; }
  .section-tag {
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--red);
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }
  .section-tag::before {
    content: '';
    width: 24px; height: 1px;
    background: var(--red);
    display: inline-block;
  }
  h2 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  /* ── ABOUT ── */
  #about {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 6rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .about-text p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.85;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .about-text p strong { color: var(--white); font-weight: 700; }
  .highlight-box {
    background: var(--card);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--red);
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--amber);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .about-visual {
    position: relative;
  }
  .toxic-lake {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border-radius: 0;
    position: relative;
    background: var(--card);
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(230,57,70,0.2);
  }
  .lake-layer {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid;
  }
  .lake-layer:nth-child(1) {
    inset: 15%;
    border-color: rgba(230,57,70,0.6);
    background: rgba(230,57,70,0.05);
    animation: lake-breathe 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .lake-layer:nth-child(2) {
    inset: 30%;
    border-color: rgba(244,162,97,0.5);
    background: rgba(244,162,97,0.05);
    animation: lake-breathe 4s ease-in-out infinite 0.7s;
  }
  .lake-layer:nth-child(3) {
    inset: 43%;
    border-color: rgba(230,57,70,0.8);
    background: rgba(230,57,70,0.15);
    animation: lake-breathe 4s ease-in-out infinite 1.4s;
  }
  @keyframes lake-breathe {
    0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.7; }
    50%       { transform: scale(1.04); opacity: 1; }
  }
  .lake-text-center {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .lake-text-center .big { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 2rem; color: var(--red); }
  .lake-text-center .small { font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 2px; margin-top: 0.3rem; }
  .corner-info {
    position: absolute;
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .corner-info.tl { top: 1rem; left: 1rem; }
  .corner-info.tr { top: 1rem; right: 1rem; text-align: right; }
  .corner-info.bl { bottom: 1rem; left: 1rem; }
  .corner-info.br { bottom: 1rem; right: 1rem; text-align: right; }
  .corner-info span { display: block; color: var(--amber); font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; }

  /* ── TIMELINE ── */
  #timeline { background: var(--card); }
  #timeline h2 { margin-bottom: 4rem; }
  .timeline-list { position: relative; padding-left: 2rem; }
  .timeline-list::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0;
    width: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--red), transparent);
  }
  .tl-item {
    position: relative;
    padding: 0 0 3.5rem 3.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateX(-20px);
    transition: opacity 0.6s, transform 0.6s;
  }
  .tl-item.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
  .tl-dot {
    position: absolute;
    left: -0.45rem;
    top: 0.15rem;
    width: 0.9rem;
    height: 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--red);
    border: 2px solid var(--navy);
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(230,57,70,0.5);
  }
  .tl-item:last-child .tl-dot { background: var(--amber); box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(244,162,97,0.5); }
  .tl-year {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--red);
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .tl-item:last-child .tl-year { color: var(--amber); }
  .tl-title {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .tl-body {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 650px;
  }

  /* ── THREATS ── */
  #threats { position: relative; }
  #threats::before {
    content: 'УГРОЗА';
    position: absolute;
    top: 3rem; right: 2rem;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14vw;
    color: rgba(230,57,70,0.04);
    pointer-events: none;
    letter-spacing: 5px;
  }
  .threats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  .threat-card {
    background: var(--card);
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
  }
  .threat-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); border-color: rgba(230,57,70,0.4); }
  .threat-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 2px;
  }
  .threat-card.red::before   { background: var(--red); }
  .threat-card.amber::before { background: var(--amber); }
  .threat-card.teal::before  { background: var(--teal); }
  .threat-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
  }
  .threat-title {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }
  .threat-body {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }
  .threat-body strong { color: var(--amber); font-weight: 700; }

  /* ── CASPIAN ── */
  #caspian { background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--navy) 0%, #0a1520 100%); }
  .caspian-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  .caspian-main p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.85;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .caspian-main p strong { color: var(--white); }
  .alert-box {
    background: rgba(230,57,70,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(230,57,70,0.4);
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .alert-box::before {
    content: '⚠ ИНЦИДЕНТ';
    position: absolute;
    top: -0.7rem;
    left: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--red);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
  }
  .alert-box p {
    font-size: 0.9rem !important;
    color: var(--white) !important;
    margin: 0 !important;
  }
  .caspian-sidebar { position: sticky; top: 8rem; }
  .sidebar-card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid rgba(78,205,196,0.2);
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .sidebar-card h4 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .fact-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    padding: 0.6rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
  }
  .fact-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .fact-label { color: var(--muted); }
  .fact-val { color: var(--white); font-weight: 700; font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace; }
  .fact-val.red { color: var(--red); }
  .fact-val.amber { color: var(--amber); }

  /* ── WATER METER ── */
  .water-meter {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid rgba(230,57,70,0.2);
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  .water-meter h4 {
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: var(--red);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .meter-row { margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
  .meter-label { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; }
  .meter-label span { color: var(--white); font-weight: 700; }
  .meter-bar { height: 6px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border-radius: 3px; overflow: hidden; }
  .meter-fill {
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 3px;
    animation: fill-bar 1.5s ease-out forwards;
    transform-origin: left;
  }
  @keyframes fill-bar { from { width: 0; } }
  .meter-fill.red   { background: var(--red); }
  .meter-fill.amber { background: var(--amber); }
  .meter-fill.teal  { background: var(--teal); }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    background: #080f18;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(230,57,70,0.2);
    padding: 4rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: end;
  }
  .footer-logo {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: var(--red);
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }
  .footer-tagline {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 380px;
  }
  .footer-right { text-align: right; }
  .footer-sources h5 {
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: var(--red);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .footer-sources ul { list-style: none; }
  .footer-sources li {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .footer-sources li::before { content: '— '; }
  .footer-copy {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: rgba(123,150,178,0.5);
    text-align: center;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  /* ── SCROLL ANIMATIONS ── */
  .fade-in {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
  }
  .fade-in.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    nav { padding: 1rem 2rem; }
    .nav-links { gap: 1.5rem; }
    section { padding: 5rem 2rem; }
    #hero { padding: 0 2rem; }
    #stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    #about { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
    .about-visual { max-width: 380px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .threats-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .caspian-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
    .caspian-sidebar { position: static; }
    footer { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    .footer-right { text-align: left; }
    #threats::before { display: none; }
    .rings { width: 280px; height: 280px; right: -2%; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">☢ КОШКАР-АТА</div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">О проблеме</a></li>
    <li><a href="#timeline">Хроника</a></li>
    <li><a href="#threats">Угрозы</a></li>
    <li><a href="#caspian">Каспий</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>

  <div class="rings">
    <div class="ring"></div>
    <div class="ring"></div>
    <div class="ring"></div>
    <div class="ring"></div>
    <div class="rad-symbol">
      <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none">
        <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="10" fill="#E63946"/>
        <path d="M50 40 A10 10 0 0 0 41.3 45 L15 30 A40 40 0 0 1 50 10 Z" fill="#E63946" opacity="0.9"/>
        <path d="M41.3 55 A10 10 0 0 0 50 60 L50 90 A40 40 0 0 1 14 70 Z" fill="#E63946" opacity="0.9"/>
        <path d="M58.7 55 A10 10 0 0 0 58.7 45 L85 30 A40 40 0 0 1 86 70 Z" fill="#E63946" opacity="0.9"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-tag">Экологическая катастрофа · Казахстан</div>
    <h1>КОШКАР-<span>АТА</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-desc">
      105 миллионов тонн токсичных и радиоактивных отходов.
      В 8 км от Каспийского моря. В 5 км от города с населением 176 000 человек.
      Рекультивация длится более 20 лет.
    </p>
